---

<DocsLayout title="Docs" nav={nav}>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">

    <!-- INTRODUCTION -->
    <section id="introduction" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">
        Astro + Tailwind CSS
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
        Astro Showcase Template
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Un générateur de site vitrine <strong class="text-gray-700">data-driven</strong> — composez vos pages section par section, tout depuis un seul fichier TypeScript.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { title: '10 sections', desc: 'Hero, Features, Stats, CTA, Text, Testimonials, ImageText, FAQ, ContactInfo, Logos' },
          { title: '1 fichier', desc: 'Tout le contenu — textes, pages, styles — dans site.ts' },
          { title: '0 CMS', desc: "Pas de base de données, pas d'interface d'admin" },
        ].map(card => (
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-1">{card.title}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">{card.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- PRÉREQUIS -->
    <section id="prerequis" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Prérequis</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Ce qu'il faut avoir installé sur votre machine avant de commencer.</p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 font-bold text-sm">N</div>
          <div class="min-w-0">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Node.js <span class="font-normal text-gray-400">v18 ou supérieur</span></p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-0.5 mb-3">
              Téléchargez sur <a href="https://nodejs.org" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">nodejs.org</a> (version LTS recommandée).
              Sur macOS/Linux, <a href="https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">nvm</a> permet de gérer plusieurs versions facilement.
            </p>
            <Code code={`node --version   # doit afficher v18.x.x ou supérieur\nnpm --version    # npm est inclus avec Node`} lang="bash" theme="github-light" class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden text-xs" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-700 font-bold text-sm">G</div>
          <div class="min-w-0">
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Git</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-0.5 mb-3">Pour cloner le projet. Téléchargez sur <a href="https://git-scm.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">git-scm.com</a>.</p>
            <Code code={`git --version    # doit afficher git version 2.x.x`} lang="bash" theme="github-light" class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden text-xs" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 font-bold text-sm">✎</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Un éditeur de code</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-0.5">
              <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">VS Code</a> est recommandé, avec l'extension
              <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=astro-build.astro-vscode" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank">Astro</a> pour la coloration syntaxique.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- INSTALLATION -->
    <section id="installation" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Installation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Trois commandes pour avoir le site en local.</p>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">1 — Cloner le repo</p>
          <Code code={`git clone https://github.com/G0nni/astro-showcase-template.git mon-site\ncd mon-site`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">2 — Installer les dépendances</p>
          <Code code={`npm install`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">3 — Lancer le serveur de développement</p>
          <Code code={`npm run dev`} lang="bash" theme="github-dark" class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden" />
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Ouvrez <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">http://localhost:4321</code> dans votre navigateur.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- STRUCTURE -->
    <section id="structure" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Structure du projet</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Les seuls dossiers que vous aurez besoin de toucher.</p>
      <Code
        code={`mon-site/\n├── src/\n│   ├── config/\n│   │   └── site.ts        ← ⭐ Le seul fichier à modifier\n│   ├── pages/\n│   │   ├── index.astro    ← Cette page de docs\n│   │   ├── about.astro    ← Page À propos\n│   │   ├── contact.astro  ← Page Contact\n│   │   └── services.astro ← Page Services\n│   └── components/        ← Ne pas modifier\n├── public/\n│   └── favicon.svg        ← Remplacez par votre favicon\n└── astro.config.mjs       ← À modifier pour le déploiement`}
        lang="bash"
        theme="github-dark"
        class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
      />
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- ÉDITER SITE.TS -->
    <section id="editer" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Éditer <code class="font-mono text-blue-600">site.ts</code></h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">
        Chaque page est une liste de sections. Chaque section a un <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-xs">type</code>, des <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-xs">props</code> et un <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-xs">style</code> optionnel.
      </p>
      <Code
        code={`// src/config/site.ts\nexport const siteConfig = {\n  global: {\n    name: "Mon Site",\n    url: "https://monsite.fr",\n  },\n  navigation: [\n    { label: "Accueil", href: "/" },\n    { label: "Contact", href: "/contact" },\n  ],\n  pages: {\n    home: {\n      seo: { title: "Accueil", description: "..." },\n      sections: [\n        {\n          type: "hero",\n          props: {\n            title: "Mon titre",\n            subtitle: "Mon sous-titre",\n            ctaPrimary: { label: "Contact", href: "/contact" },\n          },\n        },\n        {\n          type: "features",\n          style: { background: "light" },\n          props: { title: "Nos services", items: [...] },\n        },\n        {\n          type: "cta",\n          style: { background: "gradient" },\n          props: { title: "Démarrer ?", cta: { label: "Oui", href: "/contact" } },\n        },\n      ],\n    },\n  },\n};`}
        lang="ts"
        theme="github-dark"
        class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
      />
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- CRÉER UNE PAGE -->
    <section id="nouvelle-page" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Créer une nouvelle page</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Deux étapes : déclarer la page dans <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">site.ts</code>, créer le fichier <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">.astro</code>.</p>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">1 — Ajouter dans site.ts</p>
          <Code
            code={`pages: {\n  // ... pages existantes ...\n  services: {\n    seo: { title: "Services", description: "Nos prestations" },\n    sections: [\n      { type: "text",     props: { title: "Nos services", paragraphs: ["..."] } },\n      { type: "features", props: { title: "Ce que l'on fait", items: [...] } },\n      { type: "faq",      props: { items: [...] } },\n      { type: "cta",      style: { background: "dark" }, props: { ... } },\n    ],\n  },\n}`}
            lang="ts"
            theme="github-dark"
            class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">2 — Créer src/pages/services.astro</p>
          <Code
            code={`---\nimport BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';\nimport SectionRenderer from '../components/SectionRenderer.astro';\nimport { siteConfig } from '../config/site';\n\nconst page = siteConfig.pages.services;\n---\n\n<BaseLayout title={page.seo.title} description={page.seo.description} pathname="/services">\n  {page.sections.map(block => <SectionRenderer block={block} />)}\n</BaseLayout>`}
            lang="astro"
            theme="github-dark"
            class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
          />
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">La page est accessible à <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">/services</code>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-100 mb-16" />

    <!-- STYLES -->
    <section id="styles" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personnaliser les styles</h2>
